    Get platforms



            2.0






        Get all available platforms on Soundcharts.


        Please note that we do not get data on all platforms for all endpoints.


        This endpoint is useful to be sure to get all identifiers for artists/songs/albums/radios.
            To do this, use the Get IDs endpoint for artists, Get IDs for songs or Get IDs for albums or Get IDs for radios endpoints.



            For more granularity, use the Get platforms for audience data or the Get platforms for streaming data endpoints.



